Product Description:
- Frudia Citrus Brightening Cream 55g will leave your skin glowing.
- Due to a vitamin-rich formula with 61% of Citrus Extract, this cream brightens up dark spots such as blemishes and freckles and revives dull skin while evening the tone.
- On top of this, this tangerine brightening cream has a texture that makes for an easy application that leaves the skin feeling smooth and moist.
- Within four weeks, you'll be able to see the results: improved brightness and decreased melanin and pigmentation effects!
Product Features:
:: Texture: cream;
:: Skin issues: dull skin, blemishes and freckles;
:: Time of application: morning and/or evening;
:: Age: 16+;
:: Skin type: all skin types, including sensitive;
- Main benefits: brightens the skin, reduces dark spots;
:: Formulated without: alcohol.
How to Use:
- Apply Frudia Citrus Brightening Cream 55g at the last step of your skincare routine.
- Apply a suitable amount and gently tap it until the skin absorbs it completely.
Ingredients:
- Citrus Unshiu Peel Extract (61%) is rich in Vitamin C. Therefore, it has a whitening and brightening effect on the skin, while aiding skin repair;
- Niacinamide, known as vitamin B3, has many skin benefits. From fading brown spots to increasing ceramide synthesis which results in skin hydration and a stronger skin barrier. In this product, it is responsible for brightening the skin;
- Glycerin is a natural moisturizer present in our skin. It has been used for more than half a century, not as a mere moisturizer but also to protect the skin against irritation. Additionally, it keeps the skin healthy, restoring its barrier. It is effective from low percentages.
